   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Buy a Brick - Build a new HOME</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">COVID-19 hit the restaurant industry in Vietnam hard. With lockdown and no international tourists, we sadly had to close KOTO Training Restaurant at 59 Van Mieu. Since the future of the tourism industry hangs in the balance, it&apos;s not a viable strategy for KOTO to &quot;sit and wait it out&quot;.   We hope you consider supporting KOTO by being one of the first to &quot;Buy a Brick - Build a new HOME&quot; for our new restaurant, all funds will go towards building KOTO Villa which will be a new home for the trainees.</narrative>
  </description>
